drm (0.4.9) jaunty; urgency=low

  * Remove 'Quit' button (it was redundant).
  * Add new options to toggle automatic scan for roms archives at
    startup and when DAT file got updated.
  * Add an 'Extract in' option to select a default extract directory
    for archives.
  * Add a new item in list treeview popup menu, to extract archives
    in the default directory.
  * Update translations.

 -- Fortunato Ventre (voRia) <vorione@gmail.com>  Thu, 02 Jul 2009 15:02:27 +0200

drm (0.4.8) jaunty; urgency=low

  * Resize images to 50% if vertical screen resolution is <= 600,
    to 75% if vertical screen resolution <= 800.
    For bigger resolutions use the native size. 

 -- Fortunato Ventre (voRia) <vorione@gmail.com>  Wed, 01 Jul 2009 16:39:12 +0200

