 -- Fortunato Ventre (voRia) <vorione@gmail.com>  Wed, 01 Jul 2009 15:17:45 +0200

drm (0.4.7) jaunty; urgency=low

  * Disable 'Rebuild' option in treeview popup menu, if another rebuild
    process is up and running.
  * Changed icon in games list for rebuildable games from
    gtk.STOCK_DIALOG_WARNING to gtk.STOCK_CONVERT.
  * Use smaller icons in games list.
  * Added multiple selection support in games list, allowing more games
    to be selected and extracted/rebuilded at once.
  * When rebuilding roms archives, update on the fly the relative entries
    in games list.
  * Redirect program's output in a log file, $HOME/.dsromsmanager/log.
  * Avoid multiple running instance through the launcher script.
  * Do better checks when scanning for roms on hard disk.
  * Do better sanity checks when changing options.
  * Add the 'Rescan archives' button, to rescan roms archives and reload
    games list.
  * Update images paths in database when "Images" path has been changed
    in options.
  * When filters are clear and games list is not dirty, pressing the
    'clear' button will unselect current selection(s) in treeview.
  * Add tooltips in statusicon popup menu.
  * Add tooltips in treeview popup menu.
  * Add a quit button.
  * Update translations. 

 -- Fortunato Ventre (voRia) <vorione@gmail.com>  Wed, 01 Jul 2009 15:01:49 +0200

